name: God;Please;Save;Me
description:
if you know Evangelion series (including Rebuild), you must be knew how Shinji have to deal with the world around him. And yes, through this toy photo I want to express my feeling about the world around me. A world where some people make me down and almost make feel so depressed, also unsupported parents about my future.

I feel that I lost the fight, but I see a small light that help me to survive. I tried to visualize it through this photo, by using Eva-01 as a model.

If you felt the same, I wish you can survive.
